@Node "2_Install_Man" "MANUAL!  Ooer indeedy missus! Fnaar fnaar!"

                  @{b}ÀMÀAÀNÀUÀAÀLÀ ÀIÀNÀSÀTÀAÀLÀLÀAÀTÀIÀOÀNÀ@{ub}

  Well  it's  really easy, init?  Just drag the TrinityPlayer directory to
  anywhere on your harddrive and it'll be copied across.  That's basically
  all there is to it.

  An  LZX  archive  containing  loads  of  CD ID's is supplied in the main
  Trinity  Player  archive  for  you.   Just  un-archive it to the "Discs"
  directory  and  if you insert any CD that has an ID in there, then it'll
  automatically be loaded into @{i}Trinity Player@{ui} (registered version only).
@EndNode

