@Node "5_MailingList" "The Trinity Player Mailing List"

                         @{b}ÀMÀAÀIÀLÀIÀNÀGÀ ÀLÀIÀSÀTÀ@{ub}

  You  can  subscribe  to  the @{i}Trinity Player Mailing List@{ui} for info on the
  latest  updates,  fixes  and  things.  Send an email to me in the @{"Author" link "5_Author"}
  section  with  the subject as @{b}@{fg shine}TP-SUBSCRIBE@{fg text}@{ub},  then you'll be added to it.
  Which  means  that  you'll  be  the  first  to  hear of any annoucements
  regarding @{i}TP@{ui}!  Huzzah!

  Don't  worry,  there  won't be any noticable email traffic or anything -
  you'll  only  receive  the  latest  news/annoucements regardling @{i}Trinity@{ui}
  @{i}Player@{ui}, so it's not going to flood your in-box!
@EndNode

